porting. the Cathedral of Learning — brick by brick, by hand -
to the State College campus, where it will be rebuilt in the shape
of a giant kitty cat, er, Nrttany Lion. ,

- We will humbly accept a win Saturday in exchange for a
winless record to follow for the rest of the season. In exchange
